title: Arsene Wenger: Arsenal need strong start against Bayern Munich - Gazette-news.co.uk
text:
Manager Arsene Wenger knows it would be crazy to believe Arsenal can simply blow away the best team in the world, but sees no reason why his side cannot match Bayern Munich in their Champions League showdown. The German giants come to the Emirates Stadium on Tuesday night in imperious form, having just set a record for the best start to a domestic season with their ninth consecutive Bundesliga victory.
 Gazette-news.co.uk.
